{"hf446fc7cgede2g434eg9e04g93f5ccab3e8c": ["I had a friend who had a dog once. Beautiful animal, but it got mean in its old days.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "7293b1ba-c892-424f-979a-6d7c1ff9d99e"], "hea81c153gd1d5g44f6ga8c1g5151b35d17bd": ["It would growl and bark at everyone. Even bit him at the end.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "4b568e78-bf32-ea23-bde4-08826e532455"], "h34b47271ge807g41f0ga347gabc5fd66053f": ["Yet still it was the saddest of occasions when he took the dog away for good.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "d1ab18f9-d02e-e657-0ead-70aec99018bb"], "h830ce441ge8dag40a5g9a63gbd4829d2c3da": ["It was for the best, I'm sure.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "084d9d14-2d14-4d34-bb2d-0537a40cbc32"], "h806e1edbg3c1cg4e21gbeadgd1bbb334f726": ["I'm not sure the dog would agree.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "00e6dbb4-f5d8-4e08-9dbf-29db0f3fcb9e"], "h28422910g9704g49cdga6d9g454cf2ffb3a7": ["Astarion wouldn't. I'm absolutely sure of that.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "c458ff93-f10a-9ef1-2305-a96620a0b99a"], "hc65f3957g8841g44e1gac4cg5c99b9585a1a": ["Parting is never easy.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "c94167d0-99dd-4db3-ba3a-00b7de530571"], "h04875a5cg0999g47dcgba1dg96ecaf0625e1": ["Isn't it? You just made it look quite easy though.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "13fea4f5-76eb-467c-bdd7-6742c0d70969"], "h83647987g19c9g4732g8642gfeff8ad6e44d": ["Put the mongrel down, did he?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "2dd8813b-f51c-2fc9-ee5e-56c1f4b2c61a"], "he39f7c50gbcabg4d16g809dg83ed82ff09fb": ["Is that the dog you're referring to, or Astarion?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "72a4353e-65c3-4800-de35-17d8e7e754d5"], "h4b61ff98g09dfg4485g9090gd61db4a394d5": ["The dog.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "b47d2edb-77e4-4ca9-9eba-6814c50dbcc6"], "he8c891c3gc8dbg4747gad17g0afa24799d34": ["Yes. He put it down.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "cbc25636-f948-137b-1805-748b497a1b24"], "h9bff1216g5cb3g4131g8227g627ab68450b7": ["Astarion.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "9c035115-813f-0b34-e51d-f6ff50868f14"], "hb9eceac1gfeddg4a39gaa62gebe9f6ca8ec5": ["They'll probably do worse than put him down.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Reflection_Dialogs\\HAG_GurHunter_RD_BetrayedAstarion_Gale.html", "002941a7-8fed-495a-9e45-bc2297a46576"]}